ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Ontario
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ONTARIO (1) the Hon. HEATHER J. SMITH from October 22 to 24, 2013, inclusive; (2) the Hon. KATHRYN N. FELDMAN from October 28 to 29, 2013 and from November 5 to 15, 2013, inclusive; (3) the Hon. PETER D. LAUWERS from November 1 to 2, 2013, inclusive; and (4) the Hon. ROBERT J. SHARPE from November 3 to 4, 2013, inclusive.
